fm: int compareTwoPeople(Person a, Person b){     if (strcmp(a.name, b.name)==0)         if (a.age==b.age)             if (a.salary==b.salary)                 return 1; 	return 0; }

int compareGroup(Person* a, Person* b, int size_a, int size_b){     if (size_a != size_b)         return 0;     else{     for (int i = 0; i < size_a; i++)         if (strcmp(a[i].name, b[i].name) !=0 || a[i].age != b[i].age || a[i].salary != b[i].salary)             return 0; 	return 1; 	} }

int compareGroup(Person a[3], Person b[3]){     for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++)         if (strcmp(a[i].name, b[i].name) !=0 || a[i].age != b[i].age || a[i].salary != b[i].salary)             return 0; 	return 1; }
